title: Rivian stock rises 15% as automaker tops Q4 expectations, targets significant production increase
summary_full: Rivian's 2026 guidance includes increasing vehicle deliveries to between 62,000 and 67,000 units, which would be up by 47% to 59% compared to 2025.
